	"%(qprep)"
	"\![*]\_a[OnQuestion.JellyfishCute2,1]Bell\_a\w8\n"
	"\![*]\_a[OnQuestion.JellyfishCute2,1]Tendril\_a\w8\n"
	"\![*]\_a[OnQuestion.JellyfishCute2,1]Mouth\_a\w8\n"
