}

OnQuestion.Fabrics : all 
{
	"%(s.smile)You mortals are so creative!\w8 You've made so many different kinds of fabrics!\w8\w8 \i[203]I wish I could make and wear clothes the way you do, but it's not like I'm corporeal, ahaha!\w8\w8 \s[2]\i[202]\i[404]All I can do is replicate the look...\w8\w8 \s[2]\i[404]Ooh!\w8 \![anim,stop,404]\i[403]\i[203]What dress should I make next, mortal?"
	"%(qprep)"
